<p>Overleaf is a web platform where you can write LaTeX and compile documents easily. Packages, environments and commands should work the same in Overleaf as in locally installed versions of LaTeX.</p>

<p>Note : EPFL members have access to the premium version of <a href="https://www.overleaf.com">Overleaf</a> if they sign up with their EPFL email address.</p>

